article_title: Two killed in accident were newly engaged
article_text:
Carrollton, GA (30117)

Today

Some sun this morning with increasing clouds this afternoon. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 87F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy skies. Low 63F. Winds light and variable.

article_metadata.author: Donny Karr/Times-Georgian

og.description: A newly engaged Carroll County couple was killed in a crash that occurred in the early morning hours of on Dec. 30 on Highway 16 in Coweta County. Alex McLeroy,
